      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been reliably maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior still shows a nice shine, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful daily driving. The interior is clean and well-kept, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and all features are fully functional, making it a dependable choice for its next owner.",
