      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously gotta see this beauty in person\u2014it is honestly an absolute gem! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s still looking and driving like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s completely spotless inside and out, and I promise it\u2019s been treated with nothing but love. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s in truly pristine shape and ready for a new home, this is the one. Come take it for a spin, I just know you\u2019re going to fall in love with it!",
