    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This AP2-generation S2000 is a superlative example of high-revving, naturally aspirated engineering. The F22C1 power plant maintains factory-spec compression, delivering a seamless VTEC transition and a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The longitudinal 6-speed manual transmission retains its legendary tactile precision with perfectly indexed synchros, sending power through a robust Torsen limited-slip differential. Underneath, the X-bone monocoque chassis is pristine, featuring original double-wishbone suspension geometry and bushings that remain compliant yet firm. Free of subframe oxidation or fluid weeping, this specimen offers the telepathic turn-in and mechanical transparency that defined the golden era of Japanese performance. A concours-ready drivetrain for the uncompromising enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
