    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a showroom-quality 2018 Audi RS5 Coupe in Nardo Gray. This vehicle is the definition of 'mint,' having been strictly garage-kept and professionally detailed weekly. The exterior paint is flawless, protected by a high-gloss ceramic coating, while the interior retains its original factory scent with absolutely zero wear on the Fine Nappa leather bolsters or carbon fiber inlays. Mechanically, the car is in peak condition, supported by a comprehensive service history performed exclusively at authorized Audi dealerships. With no modifications, no track time, and a spotless undercarriage, this is a rare opportunity to own a preserved, enthusiast-grade masterpiece that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
